						<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>How to turn a seemingly plain skirt into a luxury skirt;</li>
<li>Technique for sewing an elegant fishtail wedding skirt with veiling ruffles which are sewn to it without seam allowances;</li>
<li>What secret know-how’s and tricks can help you achieve the goal;</li>
<li>How to give the skirt good balance;</li>
<li>And, most importantly, you will go through all stages of the process: from choosing the fabrics to examining the finished garment.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Where to use:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Mermaid/Fishtail skirt is a classic type of a wedding skirt which has been and will always remain one of the most popular and sought-after garments for any bride who wants to look elegant on her special day.</li>
</ul>
